Bachelor Degree in Business or above with minimum 5 years relevant experience;
Mature, responsible, trustworthy, self-motivated and detail-oriented;
Strong communication and interpersonal skills with strong sense of responsibilities;
Excellent command in spoken and written English, Mandarin and Cantonese;
Proficiency in PC software, e.g. MS PowerPoint, Word, and Excel;
Willing to travel when required.
Interested parties, please click "Apply Now" to submit your application.


